.scbdd.com/server/interact/292711/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[3] "Product Information. Stribild (cobicistat/elvitegravir/emtricitabine/tenofov)." Gilead Sciences  (2012):', 1767363028);
