unteers." Clin Pharmacol Ther 71 (2002):  46-56[4] "Product Information. Nuvigil (armodafinil)." Cephalon Inc  (2007):[5] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[6] Faculty of Sexual & Reproductive Healthcare "FSRH Clinical Guidance: Drug Interactions with Hormonal Contraception.  file:///C:/Users/df033684/Downloads/ceuguidancedruginteractionshormonal.pdf"   (2016):', 1767363028);
